The paper discusses a database engine that focuses on capturing and processing data lineage efficiently. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Database), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also mentions optimizations for future lineage queries, which falls under cs.PL (Programming Languages) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
